From 22ad8a126693a23cead17628c646ddfd73dad415 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: HNO3Miracle <xiangao.or@isrc.iscas.ac.cn>
Date: Sun, 24 May 2026 15:38:06 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Update cloud-go APIs and fix Go test format strings

Newer cloud-go exposes the Monitoring v3 protos through
cloud.google.com/go/monitoring/apiv3/v2/monitoringpb instead of
google.golang.org/genproto/googleapis/monitoring/v3, so update the imports to
match the packaged cloud-go stack.

The previous code only used github.com/prometheus/prometheus/model/value for
the stale NaN constants and helper. Copy the equivalent constants locally to
avoid pulling the full Prometheus source dependency into this leaf exporter;
the stale NaN detection behavior is unchanged.

Current Go vet also rejects non-constant format strings passed to t.Fatalf, so
convert those call sites to regular format arguments.

